    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43064</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_062_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それにしても、いつから、誰がオレたちのこと
『英雄』とか言い出したんだろうな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So who the hell started the whole "hero" naming thing start in the first place?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43208</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_062_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さぁ……&lt;Klarth&gt;さんたちの時代でダオスを倒した
時に僕たちは英雄って呼ばれたみたいだから……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's see... I think they started naming us heroes after the defeat of Dhaos in &lt;Klarth&gt;'s era.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43300</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_062_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあ、&lt;Klarth&gt;さんが
広めたってことか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then &lt;Klarth&gt; was the one to spread the word?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43404</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_062_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>誰が広めたにしても仰々しくて、
少し戸惑う言葉だね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't think so. Whoever it was they were probably impressed at our feats and spread the word. It got out of hand quickly after...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43488</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_062_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>英雄なんて、
やっぱり重荷だ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Being a "hero" sometimes really is a burden...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43576</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_062_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>英雄なんて、もうえーゆー（えーよ）</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Seems like being a hero is all about...being a zero...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_062_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……おい、&lt;Cless&gt;、全部台無しだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>... Hey &lt;Cless&gt;. That talk fell apart quickly.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43768</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_062_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何言ってるんだ、僕はこの重い空気を
なんとかしたくて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What are you talking about! I was just trying to lighten up the mood—</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_062_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よけいに空気が重くなってる気がする……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Nope. It's confirmed. The mood just got way worse...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
